---
// The inspection entry point now lives under the session hub (S-04): the Part 1 config
// form moved to `/inspections/[id]/session/part/1` and the hub is `/inspections/[id]/session`.
// Keep this path working (the dashboard still links to `/inspections/${id}`) by redirecting
// to the session hub, which itself bounces to the Part 1 form when the config is not yet
// valid. RLS / not-found handling lives in the hub route.
const { id } = Astro.params;
return Astro.redirect(`/inspections/${id ?? ""}/session`);
